<i>adverb</i>: 은밀히 [은밀히], 은근히 [은근히], 은근슬쩍 [은근슬쩍], 슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍], 슬쩍 [슬쩍], 슬그머니 [슬그머니], 살포시 [살포시], 살짝 [살짝], 살며시 [살며시], 비밀스레 [비ː밀스레], 몰래 [몰ː래], 남몰래 [남몰래] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>은밀히 [은밀히]</dt><br>
<dd>secretly</dd><br>
<dd>숨어 있어서 겉으로 드러나지 아니하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without appearing on the surface, being hidden.</dd><br>
<dt>은근히 [은근히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. constantly and slowly</dd><br>
<dd>야단스럽지 않고 꾸준하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Steadily but not too strongly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tastefully; delicately</dd><br>
<dd>정취가 그윽하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Exquisitely.</dd><br>
<dd>3. quietly; secretly</dd><br>
<dd>행동 등이 드러나지 않고 은밀하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of behaving secretly so that others do not notice.</dd><br>
<dd>4. inwardly</dd><br>
<dd>겉으로 나타내지는 않지만 속으로 생각하는 정도가 깊고 간절하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of thinking about something deeply and sincerely even though one does not reveal it.</dd><br>
<dt>은근슬쩍 [은근슬쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>quietly; secretly; by stealth</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 슬쩍.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a stealthily manner that something is not noticed.</dd><br>
<dt>슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 잇따라 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 잇따라 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and lightly without much effort..</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 잇따라 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quietly so that others do not know..</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 잇따라 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession, carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt>슬쩍 [슬쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>Carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt>슬그머니 [슬그머니]</dt><br>
<dd>1. secretly</dd><br>
<dd>남이 잘 알아차리지 못하게 몰래.</dd><br>
<dd>In a secretive manner that other people will not realize.</dd><br>
<dd>2. inwardly</dd><br>
<dd>마음속으로 은근히.</dd><br>
<dd>Privately in one's inmost heart.</dd><br>
<dt>살포시 [살포시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. gently; softly</dd><br>
<dd>포근하게 살며시.</dd><br>
<dd>In a snug and discreet manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>남의 눈에 뜨지 않게 살짝.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a stealthy manner that it does not attract attention.</dd><br>
<dt>살짝 [살짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 아주 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dt>살며시 [살며시]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르도록 조용히 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and carefully so that others do not notice.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly; softly; cautiously</dd><br>
<dd>천천히 가볍고 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a slow, light, and careful manner.</dd><br>
<dt>비밀스레 [비ː밀스레]</dt><br>
<dd>secretly; in secret</dd><br>
<dd>무엇인가를 감추어 겉으로 드러나지 않게 하려는 면이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of concealing something so that it is not exposed.</dd><br>
<dt>몰래 [몰ː래]</dt><br>
<dd>secretly; in secret; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>남이 알지 못하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that others would not notice.</dd><br>
<dt>남몰래 [남몰래]</dt><br>
<dd>secretly</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 모르게.</dd><br>
<dd>So that others do not notice it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>